c: 2
v: 236
t: Agar tum aurton ko baghair haath lagaye aur baghair mehar muqarrar kiye tallaq dey do to bhi tum per koi gunah nahi haan unhen kuch na kuch faeeda do. Khushal apney andaz say aur tangdast apni taqat kay mutabiq dasatoor kay mutabiq acha faeeda dey. Bhalaee kerney walon per yeh lazim hai